<td>Maximum link equity transfer</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Medium</td>
<td>Relevant blogs with DR 30 to 60</td>
<td>Good equity and referral traffic</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Low</td>
<td>Small blogs and forums</td>
<td>Minimal SEO impact</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
